{"tid":726103,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然吹左好多年, 但睇來支爆好可能發生, 想知大家到果日點避難","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T13:33:26.000Z","uid":77691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"623476ce09a7027e94911f566a0199ea4e7e4f93","tid":726103,"uid":77691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"依家大陸順差減少, 人仔已經唔可以好似以前咁係咁狂印<br />\n無足夠美金支撐去印人仔, 呢幾年好多人已經由地下銀行走錢去其他國家<br />\n<br />\n雖然貶值會增加出口, 但同時5-6月又出口疲軟, 美國加關稅<br />\n大陸唔可能補貼太多, 即係出口係貶值下無乜太大得益, <br />\n總之大陸D貨得美國有能力接<br />\n<br />\n同時國內產能過剩, 靠一帶一路去清國內多餘產能, 但馬拉已經醒左<br />\n出唔到去一路, 東南亞好多國家唔妥你好耐, 中東地區又亂, 短時間好難插手太深<br />\n, 俄羅斯一直唔鍾意你中國插手中東, 唔想同你嘈先忍你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如知道一個月後會支爆, 大家點避難"},{"pid":"81e840e58642e0b6c9baf3de6e76cbd1084fe92b","tid":726103,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:29:00.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e6927855abef13e15564c44a2dce8a3a6d3cd3","tid":726103,"uid":77691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81e840e58642e0b6c9baf3de6e76cbd1084fe92b","tid":726103,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:29:00.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ba6b33a18d6542d5a407331d6ad768e24cf6ae","tid":726103,"uid":163302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"係，但今次想睇下大陸又有咩新玩法"},{"pid":"0c386c1e7ca9d2516d1e16682a29bd7b3db7e35c","tid":726103,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"其實冇乜野可以做。要做晒避險貨幣，買下美元，or黃金等。供緊樓個d就儲錢應急。"},{"pid":"253bf950ba2bf8bffbc8fe91914d543390b13bca","tid":726103,"uid":157841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim